 syslinux [linux-amd64 linux-i386],
 syslinux-common [linux-amd64 linux-i386],genisoimage
Description:  Boot Maker is a simple tool to write system image files into CD/DVD, USB flash drive and other media.
 Deepin Boot Disk Creation Tool is a system boot disk creation tool developed by the Deepin Technology team.
 It has the characteristics of simple interface and simple operation. It can help users to make deepin bootable U disk simply and conveniently.
 This tool is a cross-platform application, compatible with mac, windwos and Linux.
